 i senza legge, i condannati dalla&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px ; font-stretch: normal ; font-size: 9px ; line-height: normal ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(24 , 25 , 27) ; background-color: rgb(255 , 255 , 255)&quot;&gt;giustizia. La chiesa rappresenta uno dei capisaldi della diffusione&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px ; font-stretch: normal ; font-size: 9px ; line-height: normal ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(24 , 25 , 27) ; background-color: rgb(255 , 255 , 255)&quot;&gt;del gotico in Italia. La costruzione della basilica venne avviata nel&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px ; font-stretch: normal ; font-size: 9px ; line-height: normal ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(24 , 25 , 27) ; background-color: rgb(255 , 255 , 255)&quot;&gt;1228 da Papa Gregorio IX per poi essere consacrata&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px ; font-stretch: normal ; font-size: 9px ; line-height: normal ; font-family: &amp;#34;arial&amp;#34; ; color: rgb(24 , 25 , 27) ; background-color: rgb(255 , 255 , 255)&quot;&gt;nel 1253 da Papa Innocenzo IV.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;fontSize=9;" vertex="1" parent="1">
